Package edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.disjoint_set

Class UpTreeDisjointSetForest<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.disjoint_set.UpTreeDisjointSetForest<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of elements stored in the disjoint set
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DisjointSetForest<E>
    public class UpTreeDisjointSetForest<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements DisjointSetForest<E>
    The UpTreeDisjointSetForest is implemented as a forest of linked up-trees. Using balanced union, union has worst-case runtime of O(1). Using path-compression find, find has worst-case O(logn), but over time has worst-case runtime O(log*(n)) [log-star].
    Author:
    Dr. King, Tung Tran
